<HEADLINE>
<P>
NOTRE DAME (6-4-1) DIDN'T DESERVE THIS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Just how bad would Notre Dame's record have to be for it not to receive a 
major bowl bid? Notre Dame, with a 6-4-1 record, will rake in big bucks for its 
Fiesta Bowl appearance, while more deserving teams such as Alabama (11-1) and 
Kansas State (9-2) play in lesser bowls. 
</P>
<P>
 Notre Dame brings in fans and has a strong football tradition, but this squad 
has no Gipp or Lujack or Hornung or Montana.Notre Dame's 1994 team should have 
had to earn its way to a major bowl the way that every other team in the nation 
had to. 
</P>
<P>
 It damages the integrity of the entire bowl structure, the NCAA and the 
coalition to show one team such preferential treatment. 
</P>
<P>
 RICH WILLIAMS 
</P>
<P>
 El Centro 
</P>
