Wild Art; Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA122494-0038 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 110947 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 24, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 1; Column 2; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
