<P>
WEEKEND TV; THEMES OF CHRISTMAS AROUND THE DIAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By N.F. MENDOZA 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Not surprisingly, the weekend is filled with holiday fare. Chances are there's 
holiday-related programming on just about every hour. 
</P>
<P>
 Some of the holiday and other programming: 
</P>
<P>
 Public Affairs: TODAY: "Today" features Christmas in Hollywood; assembling 
Christmas toys; last-minute gifts; singer Walter Charles; Bon Jovi, 6 a.m. 
(4)(39)(36). . . .  
</P>
<P>
