9:30 a.m., 9:30 p.m. CNN. . . . 
</P>
<P>
 Religion in public life is the topic on "Newsmaker Saturday," with the Rev. 
Jerry Falwell, chancellor of Liberty University, and Barry Lynn, Americans for 
Separation of Church and State, 10:30 a.m. CNN. . . . 
</P>
<P>
