<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA122494-0177 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 111086 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 24, 1994, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 4; Metro Desk 
</P>
