advertising and $3 million -- naming rights NFL licensing/merchandise $2.5 
million $2.5 million Media (national, local TV, radio) $42 million $41.5 
million Annual Expenses $62 million $53.9 million Player costs $40 million 
$31.7 million Administrative, operating costs $22 million $22.2 million 
Operating Profit $20.7 million $5.5 million * Based on an average of $31 per 
ticket 
</P>
