<P>
 Moorlach comment -- In Friday's editions, a quotation by John M.W. Moorlach 
was mistakenly included in an informational graphic summarizing reactions to 
Orange County budget cuts. Moorlach was commenting on the appointment of Thomas 
E. Daxon as interim county treasurer, not on the budget cuts. 
